wikipedia_page.main: Paul Davis Ennis (born 1 February 1990) is an English footballer who plays for FC United of Manchester.

response: On 6 February 2015, Onovwigun and Chesterfield teammate Charlie Dawes signed on a one-month loan for Conference North club Stalybridge Celtic. He made his debut the following day, coming on for Paul Ennis after 69 minutes of a 4–3 defeat to local rivals Stockport County. It proved to be his only appearance and he departed on 27 February.
